            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim the ends from your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then cut them in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
